<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
       <div class="col-md-4">
         <%= image_tag "compute.png", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
         <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
          <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
       </div>

    <div class="col-md-8">
             <p>     I am completing the Code To Success bootcamp and hope to have a career in software development in the future!</p>
  <p>             I was first intrigued by the computer science world because it has a lot to do with math and I love to do math and it is an area which I succeed in. </p>
  <p>Once I started the Code to Success program, I realized that I loved to do it. I love seeing how lines of code in a terminal can make an actual website like the ones I use everyday. I realized I could use what I learn and make something that can help people. That is what I want to do! </p>
        <p>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Draper Middle School
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Code To Success Bootcamp
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
   </div>
</div>
